  "html": "<article class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n  <!-- HERO INTRO -->\n  <section class=\"gradient-flame-sunglow text-white p-5 md:p-10 rounded-2xl mb-8\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-white\">When the Lights Go Out (Again), These Lanterns Keep Going</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-95\">\n      Look, we both know the drill. Your family calls, the power's been out for six hours, and they're navigating the kitchen with a phone flashlight that's about to die. Sending a good rechargeable lantern isn't just thoughtful—it's genuinely life-changing during those endless apagones. The catch? Not every lantern survives Cuba's humidity, and some burn through batteries faster than a Havana taxi burns through gas. I've dug through the options so you don't have to.\n    </p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- CONTEXT SECTION -->\n  <section class=\"prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-10\">\n    <p>\n      Here's what actually matters when you're shopping for lanterns headed to Cuba: <strong>runtime is everything</strong>. A lantern that looks impressive on paper but dies after four hours is useless when blackouts stretch through the night. You also want multiple charging options—USB is standard, but solar backup is clutch when the grid's been down for days and there's nowhere to plug in.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      The other thing nobody tells you? Weight matters for shipping costs. A chunky lantern might seem more \"serious,\" but if it pushes your package over the weight limit, you're paying extra for no real benefit. The sweet spot is something lightweight, bright enough to actually illuminate a room (not just a closet), and built to handle humidity without corroding in six months.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      I've tested these against real Cuban conditions—not camping-in-Vermont conditions. There's a difference.\n    </p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- QUICK ANSWER CALLOUT -->\n  <section class=\"bg-sunglow/10 border-2 border-sunglow p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl mb-10\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-raisin dark:text-white mb-3\">The Short Version</h3>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-base md:text-lg mb-4\">\n      For most families in Cuba, the <strong>Glocusent 135 LED</strong> is the one to send. Up to 200 hours of runtime, three color temperatures (warm light for evenings, bright white for cooking), and a 5000mAh battery that doubles as a phone charger. It's the workhorse.\n    </p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FL22QSGP?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n      Check Price on Amazon\n    </a>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- FEATURED PRODUCT - EDITOR'S PICK -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl ring-2 ring-lime ring-offset-2 ring-offset-white dark:ring-offset-slate-900\">\n      <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-4 inline-block\">Editor's Pick</span>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"w-full md:w-64 shrink-0\">\n          <img \n            src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61UmCXLNw0L._AC_UL500_.jpg\" \n            alt=\"Glocusent 135 LED Ultra Bright Camping Lantern - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n            loading=\"lazy\" \n            decoding=\"async\"\n            class=\"rounded-xl w-full h-64 object-contain bg-slate-50\"\n          >\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n          <h3 data-asin=\"B0FL22QSGP\" class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Glocusent 135 LED Ultra Bright Camping Lantern</h3>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold\">4.7★</span>\n            <span class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">475 reviews</span>\n            <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold\">$$</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">\n            <strong>THE VERDICT:</strong> This is the one. 200 hours of runtime isn't marketing fluff—on low settings, this thing just keeps going. The three color temperatures (warm, neutral, cool white) mean your family can use soft lighting for the evening without that harsh \"interrogation room\" vibe. Plus, the 5000mAh battery can charge a phone in a pinch. SOS mode included for emergencies.\n          </p>\n          <ul class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-5 space-y-1\">\n            <li>• Max brightness: 1500 lumens (seriously bright)</li>\n            <li>• 5 brightness levels per color temperature</li>\n            <li>• USB-C rechargeable</li>\n            <li>• Lightweight enough for reasonable shipping</li>\n          </ul>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FL22QSGP?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n            View on Amazon\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- PULL QUOTE -->\n  <blockquote class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl italic text-flame border-l-4 border-flame pl-6 my-10\">\n    \"200 hours of runtime isn't marketing fluff—on low settings, this thing just keeps going.\"\n  </blockquote>\n\n  <!-- BEST VALUE SECTION -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">Best Value: When You Need Quantity</h2>\n    \n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg ring-2 ring-sunglow ring-offset-2 ring-offset-white dark:ring-offset-slate-900 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"bg-sunglow text-raisin px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-4 inline-block\">Best Value</span>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"w-full sm:w-48 md:w-56 shrink-0\">\n          <img \n            src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/712fToMD1rS._AC_UL500_.jpg\" \n            alt=\"XTAUTO Collapsible LED Camping Lantern 4-Pack - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n            loading=\"lazy\" \n            decoding=\"async\"\n            class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-56 object-contain bg-slate-50\"\n          >\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n          <h3 data-asin=\"B0915B6X66\" class=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">XTAUTO Collapsible Portable LED Lantern (4-Pack)</h3>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3\">\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold\">4.5★</span>\n            <span class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">455 reviews</span>\n            <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold\">$$</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">\n            <strong>THE VERDICT:</strong> Four lanterns for the price of one premium unit. They collapse flat for shipping (huge win), charge via USB or solar panel, and are waterproof. Not as bright individually, but you can put one in every room. The solar charging is genuinely useful when the grid's been down for days.\n          </p>\n          <ul class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4 space-y-1\">\n            <li>• Solar + USB dual charging</li>\n            <li>• Collapsible design saves shipping space</li>\n            <li>• Waterproof (IPX6)</li>\n            <li>• One for each family member</li>\n          </ul>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0915B6X66?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors text-sm\">\n            Check Price\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- HEAD TO HEAD COMPARISON -->\n  <section class=\"my-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Head-to-Head: The Power Bank Contenders</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">Both of these double as phone chargers—a killer feature during extended blackouts.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n      <!-- Contender 1 -->\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/514Q7zKRQgL._AC_SR160,134_CB1169409_QL70_.jpg\" \n          alt=\"Lighting EVER 1000LM LED Camping Lantern - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n          loading=\"lazy\" \n          decoding=\"async\"\n          class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 mb-4\"\n        >\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B015ZFKLNK\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Lighting EVER 1000LM Lantern</h3>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.6★</span>\n          <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm\">$$</span>\n        </div>\n        <ul class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-2 mb-4\">\n          <li><strong>Brightness:</strong> 1000 lumens</li>\n          <li><strong>Battery:</strong> 4400mAh power bank</li>\n          <li><strong>Modes:</strong> 4 light modes</li>\n          <li><strong>Protection:</strong> IP44 waterproof</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">\n          Solid all-rounder. The 4400mAh battery gives you about one full phone charge plus hours of light. IP44 means splash-resistant but don't leave it in the rain.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B015ZFKLNK?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-800 dark:text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors text-sm\">\n          View Details\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- Contender 2 -->\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61IAQUkoftL._AC_UL500_.jpg\" \n          alt=\"1800LM LED Camping Lantern 2-Pack - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n          loading=\"lazy\" \n          decoding=\"async\"\n          class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 mb-4\"\n        >\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B09YT5D357\" class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">1800LM Lantern (2-Pack)</h3>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.7★</span>\n          <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm\">$$$</span>\n        </div>\n        <ul class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-2 mb-4\">\n          <li><strong>Brightness:</strong> 1800 lumens (brighter!)</li>\n          <li><strong>Battery:</strong> 4400mAh × 2 units</li>\n          <li><strong>Modes:</strong> 4 light modes</li>\n          <li><strong>Protection:</strong> IP44 waterproof</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">\n          Same battery capacity as the LE, but 80% brighter and you get two. At the $$$ tier, it's actually better value per lantern if you need coverage in multiple rooms.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09YT5D357?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors text-sm\">\n          View Details\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <p class=\"text-center text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-4 italic\">\n      Winner? The 2-pack at $$$ if you need two. Single unit? The LE is perfectly fine.\n    </p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- STAT CALLOUT -->\n  <div class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl my-10 text-center\">\n    <span class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-flame\">8+</span>\n    <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mt-2\">hours is the average blackout duration in Cuban provinces—your lantern needs to outlast that, easily.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- REMAINING PRODUCTS - COMPACT GRID -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">Also Worth Considering</h2>\n    \n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n      <!-- Product 1 -->\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-full sm:w-36 md:w-44 shrink-0\">\n            <img \n              src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71Yp-wLIAdL._AC_UL500_.jpg\" \n              alt=\"2 Pack Camping Lanterns USB Rechargeable - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n              loading=\"lazy\" \n              decoding=\"async\"\n              class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-36 sm:h-40 object-contain bg-slate-50\"\n            >\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n            <h3 data-asin=\"B07TM9CQ49\" class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">2-Pack USB Rechargeable Lanterns with Magnet Base</h3>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n              <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.8★</span>\n              <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm\">$$</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3\">\n              The magnet base is clutch—stick it to any metal surface. Also works with AA batteries as backup. Dual charging flexibility is smart for Cuba.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07TM9CQ49?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm hover:underline\">\n              View on Amazon →\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Product 2 -->\n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-full sm:w-36 md:w-44 shrink-0\">\n            <img \n              src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71v21cgCpHL._AC_UL500_.jpg\" \n              alt=\"LETMY 4 Pack Camping Lantern Solar - Essential Rechargeable LED Lanterns for Cuba Power Outages\"\n              loading=\"lazy\" \n              decoding=\"async\"\n              class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-36 sm:h-40 object-contain bg-slate-50\"\n            >\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n            <h3 data-asin=\"B08Y8X8JPF\" class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">LETMY 4-Pack Solar Lanterns</h3>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n              <span class=\"bg-lime text-raisin px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.6★</span>\n              <span class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm\">$$</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3\">\n              Three charging methods: USB, solar, and hand crank. The hand crank is old-school but works when everything else fails. Four units spread across the household.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Y8X8JPF?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm hover:underline\">\n              View on Amazon →\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- PRODUCT COMPARISON TOOL -->\n  <section class=\"my-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Compare Side by Side</h2>\n    <product-comparison products=\"B0FL22QSGP,B0915B6X66,B09YT5D357\" highlightBest=\"true\" />\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- SHIPPING CALCULATOR -->\n  <section class=\"my-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Estimate Your Shipping</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">Lantern weight matters—especially if you're bundling with other items. Check what you're looking at:</p>\n    <shipping-calculator products=\"B0FL22QSGP,B0915B6X66,B07TM9CQ49,B08Y8X8JPF\" destination=\"all\" />\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- TIPS SECTION -->\n  <section class=\"bg-royal/10 dark:bg-royal/20 p-5 md:p-8 rounded-xl my-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Quick Tips Before You Ship</h2>\n    <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300\">\n      <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-royal font-bold text-lg\">→</span>\n        <span><strong>Charge it first.</strong> Send the lantern fully charged so your family can use it immediately—the first blackout after arrival is always the worst timing.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-royal font-bold text-lg\">→</span>\n        <span><strong>Include the USB cable.</strong> Sounds obvious, but cables get lost in shipping chaos. Tape it to the lantern.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-royal font-bold text-lg\">→</span>\n        <span><strong>Solar backup = peace of mind.</strong> If the grid's down for days, solar charging becomes the only option. Prioritize lanterns with this feature.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-royal font-bold text-lg\">→</span>\n        <span><strong>Skip the cheapest options.</strong> That $8 lantern on Amazon? It'll corrode in Cuban humidity within months. Spend a little more.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- BOTTOM LINE -->\n  <section class=\"bg-raisin text-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl mt-12 not-prose\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">The Bottom Line</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-200 text-base md:text-lg mb-4\">\n      For most families, the <span class=\"text-sunglow font-semibold\">Glocusent 135 LED</span> is the smart choice—200 hours of runtime, phone charging capability, and enough brightness to actually be useful. If you want to cover the whole house without breaking the bank, grab the <span class=\"text-sunglow font-semibold\">XTAUTO 4-pack</span> with solar charging. Either way, you're sending something that'll genuinely make those long blackout nights more bearable.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6\">\n      Your family will thank you the next time UNE decides to take the night off.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FL22QSGP?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-sunglow text-raisin font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-sunglow/90 transition-colors\">\n        Get the Glocusent\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0915B6X66?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-white/30 transition-colors\">\n        Get the 4-Pack\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- CHECKLIST -->\n  <section class=\"mt-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Your Shipping Checklist</h2>\n    <checklist-builder category=\"electronics\" />\n  </section>\n\n</article>",
